структура возвращаемая getcomments (см. http://code.livejournal.org/trac/livejournal/browser/trunk/cgi-bin/ljprotocol.pl):
(:|pages|)
(:|comments|
	(:|datepostunix|)
	(:|is_loaded|)
	(:|is_show|)
	(:|datepost|)
	(:|postername|)
	(:|dtalkid|)
	(:|level|)
	(:|subject|)
	(:|body|)
	(:|state|)
	(:|posterid|)
	(:|children|))


